Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    ThisItem.Index <= SelectedItem.Index,
    Timeline.AccentColor,
    ColorFade(
        Timeline.Style.Palette.Fillable,
        -10%
    )
)

If(
    ThisItem.Index = 0,
    Color.Transparent,
    If(
        ThisItem.Index <= SelectedItem.Index,
        Timeline.AccentColor,
        ColorFade(
            Timeline.Style.Palette.Fillable,
            -10%
        )
    )
)

If(
    ThisItem.Index < SelectedItem.Index,
    Timeline.AccentColor,
    If(
        ThisItem.Index < Timeline.Count - 1,
        ColorFade(
            Timeline.Style.Palette.Fillable,
            -10%
        ),
        Color.Transparent
    )
)

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(320, Self.Width - 60), Min(320, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
With(
    {rows: CountRows(Self.AllItems)},
    If(
        rows > 0,
        Self.Width / rows,
        0
    )
)
